{"tid":2094732,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"讀信捱過鐵窗生活 放監獲百人迎接  出獄手足感動：在囚者沒被遺忘","createTime":"2020-07-05T02:06:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T10:35:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":67,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b23ad985f3e1dc3d5fea51e83d86020622af45b9","tid":2094732,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T02:06:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200705/2AZ4IPAO2ODCKX6VRZG5OPHU3M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200705%2F2AZ4IPAO2ODCKX6VRZG5OPHU3M%2F&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmgKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=b2cb21b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200705%2F2AZ4IPAO2ODCKX6VRZG5OPHU3M%2F&h=cda247a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200705/2AZ4IPAO2ODCKX6VRZG5OPHU3M/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n讀信捱過鐵窗生活 放監獲百人迎接 <br />\n出獄手足感動：在囚者沒被遺忘<br />\n<br />\n【兩制蓋棺】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】「撐手足、撐到底！」6.12一周年早上，近百人於攝氏30多度烈日高溫下，在監獄外靜候同路人。有人捧着鮮花，有人揮動「光復香港、時代革命」旗幟，1B手足（化名）就是當日出獄的抗爭者。經歷逾半年的囚禁，人生因此改寫，但他從不後悔，僅因不能與其他前線抗爭者齊上齊落感遺憾。面對未來不安，他寄語同路人要堅持，更想與獄中抗爭者說：「好多人都冇忘記身在監獄嘅佢哋。」<br />\n<br />\n記者在6月底相約1B於金鐘添馬公園進行訪問，當日是他出獄後首次踏足此地。金鐘是他投身運動的起點，6月9日他參與民陣百萬人大遊行，經歷6.12中信大廈圍困、8.31太子站事件等。面對各種警暴，迫使他越走越前，和理非轉變成勇武，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n訪問當日，以一身全黑打扮重臨舊地的他，慨嘆天橋由以往貼滿文宣，現今卻水馬圍城，「好似好驚市民喺呢度表達意見」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/iDJR0Ih2bhS9dJpC3ep7No_GNBs=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OEVACHLKZHUL7EVSALVPYLEYUI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FiDJR0Ih2bhS9dJpC3ep7No_GNBs%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOEVACHLKZHUL7EVSALVPYLEYUI.jpg&h=0015fe9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n面對港版國安法，案件或會引渡內地審理，作為曾被囚人士屬高危一族，1B坦言感到害怕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qB4skepdqiDnh4i7BSIZk50Qgjo=/624x734/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OJ7TN3FI7RS73ETCKGE7AEYJBM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FqB4skepdqiDnh4i7BSIZk50Qgjo%3D%2F624x734%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOJ7TN3FI7RS73ETCKGE7AEYJBM.gif&h=850f9bc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每月逢21及31日，1B手足都會重看信件及聖誕卡，這亦是他繼續堅持的動力。 受訪者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/W8X8N4zJrRoqV5aodi1ZQyz949s=/487x591/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NM256KELXVM27ZI3DO3OTPOJYI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FW8X8N4zJrRoqV5aodi1ZQyz949s%3D%2F487x591%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNM256KELXVM27ZI3DO3OTPOJYI.gif&h=86fe8dcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在眾多聖誕卡中，1B最深刻是收到一位8歲小朋友所畫的「齊上齊落」。 受訪者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自責未能齊上齊落<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：職員指覆檢大量書籍從未見 或歷時半年<br />\n<br />\n由到庭應訊到身陷牢獄，1B最自責是未能與其他前線抗爭者齊上齊落，「我係好對唔住出面手足！」他透露，在荔枝角收押所還柙不久，便發生中大、理大兩場「戰役」，而該段時間是獄中最難捱日子。鐵窗之內，他只能透過電視、《蘋果日報》關注抗爭發展，一幕幕的警暴映入眼簾，他最擔心仍是一眾在外抗爭者。他坦言，當被迫成為旁觀者，猶如背棄手足，令他沮喪，「一接觸到濫捕消息，我返去（囚室）靜靜流眼淚」。<br />\n<br />\n他曾與囚友討論7.21、8.31事件，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n他最怕被人遺忘，當收到鐵窗外寄來的信件、聖誕卡，便很開心，「原來冇人忘記佢哋」。<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n他憶起一踏出大門，看到近百人迎接，第一反應是驚嚇，加上保護家人，只好急急腳離開，「都有感動，原來大家冇忘記我。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冀港人捐612基金<br />\n<br />\n離開監獄後，他退下前線，轉而擔任「出獄師」，支援在囚人士，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n他認同，發展黃色經濟圈可延續運動，卻不能藉此變成快樂抗爭，「抗爭唔應該用快樂呢兩個字，𠵱家拉咗9,000幾人」。<br />\n <br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n。他寄語同路人切勿忘記這班抗爭者，除支持黃色經濟圈、寫信及聽審外，亦盡所能捐款予612基金等機構，支援被捕人士法律費用等。無論將來如何，只要他一息尚存，也會抗爭到底。<br />\n<br />\n===============<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7ba5e9d93fb0aad40d9a116376a69b428f2b5a6","tid":2094732,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T02:13:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b1592fdc8c3166d1d44c0aff7d049cc417a7d1a","tid":2094732,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T02:17:12.000Z","msg":"👊🏻👊🏻👊🏻"},{"pid":"aeef58f8ae6efa4f30c5626d1d56a79ab316852c","tid":2094732,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T02:28:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ff5d4c0a391bd8c752fe45d1fef5ee78c4ee09e","tid":2094732,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T02:30:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37bb8965d86184ae4f3eb49530e508823ddfbef5","tid":2094732,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T02:32:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d3ecb1a8cafd35f62280f9a6d6597f559c9e330","tid":2094